{"tid":413121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政黨持「殺」字道具遊行抗議　何君堯：我真的好驚，要報警了！","createTime":"2017-09-25T08:52:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T08:53:04.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9ca67e00a443c7bf7a916e7b566387a838e9b6f","tid":413121,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T08:52:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170925/s00001/31bd79f40b8cfe705e9b9b6c3d3cc2a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170925%2Fs00001%2F31bd79f40b8cfe705e9b9b6c3d3cc2a3.jpg&h=060bbb32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會議員何君堯「殺無赦」論風波未息，多個政黨上周遊行抗議，何君堯昨日於facebook分享有關遊行圖片，稱「我現在真的好驚，我要報警了！」<br />\n<br />\n社民連、人民力量和香港眾志等成員，上周三（20日）遊行到中環香港律師會會址，要求該會調查身為該會前會長何君堯的「殺無赦」言論，展開紀律聆訊和作出處分，並手持貼上「殺」字的「金腰帶」，寓意「殺人放火金腰帶」。<br />\n<br />\n事隔數天，何君堯昨晚（24日）於facebook分享該遊行相片，批評對方「恐嚇」，又稱「反對派言明要殺我，我現在真的好驚，我要報警了！」而何君堯分享的照片上，有特別註明「指明道姓的殺人」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，何君堯預告，他明晚會在電視節目訪問中講清楚「殺無赦」來龍去脈，並指摘最近攻擊他的言論，純粹是轉移視線，不會影響他反「港獨」等決心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170925/s00001/1506327331573\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170925%2Fs00001%2F1506327331573&d=07lbfwDk5yoNSV6O8FIOT8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=76ca1570\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170925%2Fs00001%2F1506327331573&h=d7c11fef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170925/s00001/1506327331573</a>"},{"pid":"b2c660c8143d3b8ccec08d2457913c16e4b0b540","tid":413121,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T08:53:04.000Z","msg":"笑撚左"}]}